20
00:02:04,582 --> 00:02:05,416
Okey.

21
00:02:16,678 --> 00:02:18,596
Kenapa saya selalu mimpi begitu?

22
00:02:19,514 --> 00:02:20,890
Padahal saya sangat bahagia.

23
00:02:31,442 --> 00:02:35,238
Shiki bukan pekerja Nonamare

24
00:02:35,321 --> 00:02:37,407
ataupun seorang Esper.

25
00:02:37,490 --> 00:02:39,284
Kenapa dia tinggal di rumah syarikat?

26
00:02:39,993 --> 00:02:42,078
Bos kata Shiki anak kawannya

27
00:02:42,162 --> 00:02:44,497
dan dia diminta jaga Shiki.

28
00:02:45,165 --> 00:02:49,127
Awalnya sukar. Shiki hampir
menyusuli suaminya ke dalam kubur.

29
00:02:49,836 --> 00:02:51,421
Jadi, Pn. Enjaku temani dia.

30
00:02:58,052 --> 00:02:59,762
Itu…

31
00:02:59,846 --> 00:03:03,141
Itu bahaya. Berikan kepada saya, ya?

32
00:03:07,228 --> 00:03:08,646
Suami awak akan pulang.

33
00:03:09,647 --> 00:03:10,648
Dia ada…

34
00:03:12,525 --> 00:03:13,443
lawatan kerja yang panjang.

35
00:03:14,652 --> 00:03:16,613
Dia ada lawatan kerja yang panjang.

36
00:03:23,369 --> 00:03:24,579
Lawatan kerja?

37
00:03:24,662 --> 00:03:26,623
Ya. Mari…

38
00:03:28,124 --> 00:03:29,500
kita tunggu dia bersama-sama.

39
00:03:30,043 --> 00:03:30,919
Okey?

40
00:03:37,258 --> 00:03:40,845
Itu cerita bohong Pn. Enjaku
untuk pastikan Shiki selamat,

41
00:03:42,138 --> 00:03:45,391
tapi yang peliknya, Shiki percaya.

42
00:03:46,100 --> 00:03:48,436
Sedikit demi sedikit, dia makin pulih.

43
00:03:50,855 --> 00:03:51,981
Siapa namanya?

44
00:03:52,065 --> 00:03:54,734
- Sasuke.
- Sasuke, ya?

45
00:03:55,318 --> 00:03:58,863
Sasuke, comelnya awak.

46
00:03:58,947 --> 00:04:01,824
Salam kenal. Ini hadiah untuk awak.

47
00:04:02,450 --> 00:04:03,868
Terima kasih.

48
00:04:03,952 --> 00:04:06,454
Tulisan kanji nama saya
"Sakura" dan "Suke". Saya Ohsuke.

49
00:04:07,121 --> 00:04:08,873
Kami mula adakan malam takoyaki

50
00:04:08,957 --> 00:04:11,000
untuk ceriakan dia.

51
00:04:12,418 --> 00:04:14,879
Jadi, ada kisah
di sebalik malam takoyaki, ya?

52
00:04:14,963 --> 00:04:17,590
Lama keadaannya stabil,

53
00:04:18,174 --> 00:04:20,635
tapi, baru-baru ini,
dia mula alami kecelaruan lagi.

54
00:04:20,718 --> 00:04:24,055
Dia sedar suaminya takkan kembali.

55
00:04:24,889 --> 00:04:27,308
Tentulah.

56
00:04:27,392 --> 00:04:30,186
Tapi, memberikan dia lelaki lain

57
00:04:30,270 --> 00:04:31,980
dan dia percaya saya suaminya

58
00:04:32,063 --> 00:04:34,565
adalah tak masuk akal juga.

59
00:04:34,649 --> 00:04:36,192
Memang tak masuk akal, bukan?

60
00:04:38,444 --> 00:04:41,114
Hanzo, apa kerja awak

61
00:04:41,197 --> 00:04:44,158
sebelum sertai Nonamare?

62
00:04:49,497 --> 00:04:52,458
Pn. Enjaku hidup serba ringkas.

63
00:04:54,794 --> 00:04:55,962
Yakah?

64
00:04:56,045 --> 00:04:57,130
UBAT GIGI CLEANEX

65
00:04:58,464 --> 00:05:01,050
Dia hanya beli barang yang ada diskaun…

66
00:05:01,134 --> 00:05:02,093
PERIBAHASA SELURUH DUNIA

67
00:05:02,176 --> 00:05:03,970
…baca buku perpustakaan,

68
00:05:04,053 --> 00:05:06,514
menulis sutra setiap hari
menggunakan pen mata bulat.

69
00:05:07,223 --> 00:05:08,099
Hidupnya murni,

70
00:05:08,182 --> 00:05:11,269
dan dia bebaskan diri daripada nafsu.

71
00:05:12,020 --> 00:05:14,939
- Dia tiada keluarga?
- Tiada.

72
00:05:15,023 --> 00:05:17,692
Sudah banyak dugaan dia tempuhi.

73
00:05:20,111 --> 00:05:22,238
Jadi, apa yang awak gunakan untuk…

74
00:05:22,322 --> 00:05:24,324
Banyaknya rumput, tak habis-habis dicabut.

75
00:05:24,407 --> 00:05:26,326
Tapi saya suka baunya.

76
00:05:26,409 --> 00:05:28,244
Bau rumput… Apa namanya?

77
00:05:29,245 --> 00:05:31,581
Bau ini! Hei, apa nama bau ini?

78
00:05:31,664 --> 00:05:33,416
Baunya berbeza bergantung pada…

79
00:05:33,499 --> 00:05:37,211
Apa? Awak nak tahu tentang Hanzo?

80
00:05:37,295 --> 00:05:38,212
Tak…

81
00:05:39,088 --> 00:05:41,507
Bukan begitu,

82
00:05:41,591 --> 00:05:44,052
tapi kalau orang sembunyikan sesuatu,
saya rasa nak tahu.

83
00:05:44,135 --> 00:05:46,512
Dia penggila haiwan.

84
00:05:46,596 --> 00:05:48,347
Itu semua orang tahu!

85
00:05:49,057 --> 00:05:52,226
Dia ambil dan bela haiwan terbiar,
dia juga ada beli beberapa ekor.

86
00:05:52,310 --> 00:05:55,188
Dia kata dia tak mampu menolak
apabila haiwan nak ikut pulang.

87
00:05:55,897 --> 00:05:59,400
Kini, dia elak pergi ke kedai haiwan.

88
00:05:59,484 --> 00:06:00,568
Maaf, Kuroda.

89
00:06:01,402 --> 00:06:02,361
Di rumah, dia hanya

90
00:06:03,029 --> 00:06:05,156
kutip najis haiwan sepanjang hari.

91
00:06:05,239 --> 00:06:06,532
Awak rasa gatal?

92
00:06:06,616 --> 00:06:07,742
Dia tiada keluargakah?

93
00:06:07,825 --> 00:06:08,659
Haiwan-haiwan itulah keluarganya.

94
00:06:08,743 --> 00:06:10,787
Itu semua orang tahu!

95
00:06:12,663 --> 00:06:14,457
Tak juga.

96
00:06:18,294 --> 00:06:19,295
Sebenarnya…

97
00:06:24,926 --> 00:06:26,052
dia pernah bunuh orang.

98
00:06:29,222 --> 00:06:32,100
Syarikat pelik, tugasan pun pelik…

99
00:06:33,851 --> 00:06:36,813
Rupa-rupanya
tiada seorang pun pekerjanya normal.

100
00:06:38,064 --> 00:06:40,483
Hidup ini memang penuh dengan kejutan.

101
00:06:41,484 --> 00:06:42,819
Apa maksud awak?

102
00:06:44,362 --> 00:06:45,696
Begini…

103
00:06:48,032 --> 00:06:49,242
Ohsuke nampak kasar,

104
00:06:49,325 --> 00:06:51,702
tapi dia bukan budak jahat.

105
00:06:52,411 --> 00:06:54,872
Dia ada kisah silamnya sendiri,

106
00:06:55,414 --> 00:06:57,875
tapi kini dia serius bekerja di Nonamare

107
00:06:57,959 --> 00:06:58,918
dan kedai bunganya.

108
00:07:00,169 --> 00:07:01,587
Dia penjual bunga dari dulu lagi?

109
00:07:01,671 --> 00:07:04,340
Tak, dia mula jual bunga
setelah menjadi Esper.

110
00:07:06,467 --> 00:07:08,678
Bos setuju

111
00:07:08,761 --> 00:07:10,513
sebab penyamaran begitu

112
00:07:10,596 --> 00:07:12,265
mungkin berguna untuk jalankan misi.

113
00:07:12,348 --> 00:07:14,809
Malah, bos sewakan kedai itu untuknya.

114
00:07:19,397 --> 00:07:21,065
Dah siap asing-asingkan.

115
00:07:22,525 --> 00:07:25,862
Cabut rumput, kutip sampah, kitar semula…

116
00:07:25,945 --> 00:07:28,030
Awak selalu buat begini?

117
00:07:28,114 --> 00:07:29,699
Ya, apabila tiada misi.

118
00:07:29,782 --> 00:07:32,785
Tindakan kecil begini pun penting
macam kerja kita.

119
00:07:33,619 --> 00:07:35,413
Kerja kita, ya?

120
00:07:37,957 --> 00:07:40,585
Dengar sini. Anda semua wira

121
00:07:40,668 --> 00:07:43,004
yang menyelamatkan dunia.

122
00:07:44,505 --> 00:07:48,342
Wira mestilah ada rasa tanggungjawab
dan etika yang kuat.

123
00:07:48,426 --> 00:07:49,260
Ya.

124
00:07:49,886 --> 00:07:50,970
Perkara sekecil

125
00:07:51,053 --> 00:07:53,681
membersihkan kejiranan kita.

126
00:07:53,764 --> 00:07:56,976
Nampak macam remeh, tapi…

127
00:07:58,644 --> 00:08:02,064
langkah kecil itulah

128
00:08:02,148 --> 00:08:03,816
yang akhirnya akan selamatkan dunia.

129
00:08:08,029 --> 00:08:08,863
Ya?

130
00:08:08,946 --> 00:08:11,741
Saya faham cita-cita tuan.

131
00:08:11,824 --> 00:08:13,201
Sungguh, tapi…

132
00:08:14,035 --> 00:08:17,121
Kalau ada matlamat yang lebih jelas,

133
00:08:17,205 --> 00:08:20,666
itu lebih mudah untuk diusahakan.

134
00:08:21,250 --> 00:08:22,084
Bunta,

135
00:08:22,835 --> 00:08:24,295
awak rasa

136
00:08:24,378 --> 00:08:27,423
kebahagiaan boleh diukur?

137
00:08:28,883 --> 00:08:31,219
Boleh awak letakkan nombor
dalam menyelamatkan dunia

138
00:08:32,094 --> 00:08:34,764
seperti wang dan jualan?

139
00:08:36,891 --> 00:08:39,685
Pemikiran begitulah yang bermasalah!

140
00:08:39,769 --> 00:08:40,853
Itu sebab awak gelapkan wang

141
00:08:40,937 --> 00:08:44,315
dan hancurkan hidup awak.

142
00:08:44,398 --> 00:08:46,692
Awak biarkan nombor mengawal pilihan awak.

143
00:08:49,445 --> 00:08:51,781
Penyakit bermula dengan pemikiran kita.

144
00:08:51,864 --> 00:08:53,407
Begitu juga dengan kewiraan.

145
00:08:55,076 --> 00:08:56,035
Itu slogankah?

146
00:08:56,118 --> 00:08:58,246
- Bunta!
- Ya?

147
00:08:58,329 --> 00:09:02,124
"Saya hanyalah sedikit Esper

148
00:09:02,208 --> 00:09:03,918
dan sedikit wira."

149
00:09:04,794 --> 00:09:05,628
Cakaplah.

150
00:09:07,380 --> 00:09:09,465
- Apa?
- "Saya…"

151
00:09:12,426 --> 00:09:16,389
Saya hanyalah sedikit Esper

152
00:09:16,472 --> 00:09:18,849
dan sedikit wira?

153
00:09:18,933 --> 00:09:20,184
Itu bukan soalan.

154
00:09:21,394 --> 00:09:24,230
Saya hanyalah sedikit Esper

155
00:09:24,313 --> 00:09:25,606
dan sedikit wira.

156
00:09:25,690 --> 00:09:27,191
Semangat lagi.

157
00:09:28,568 --> 00:09:29,986
- Saya…
- Ambil serius hal ini!

158
00:09:31,612 --> 00:09:34,532
Saya hanyalah sedikit Esper

159
00:09:34,615 --> 00:09:36,534
- dan sedikit wira!
- Dengan yakin!

160
00:09:36,617 --> 00:09:39,161
Saya hanyalah sedikit Esper
dan sedikit wira!

161
00:09:39,245 --> 00:09:41,539
- Sekali lagi!
- Saya hanyalah sedikit Esper dan…

162
00:09:55,636 --> 00:09:56,804
‎BUNTA MENGENALI OHSUKE.
‎DIA INGAT AYAHNYA.

163
00:09:56,887 --> 00:09:57,888
‎ANJING MENYALAK, CINTA BERPUTIK

164
00:09:57,972 --> 00:09:58,931
‎ESPER MENJADI SEPERTI WIRA SEDIKIT.

165
00:10:07,982 --> 00:10:09,233
Awak dah makan tadi.

166
00:10:09,775 --> 00:10:11,444
Tak boleh makan keledek lagi.

167
00:10:12,278 --> 00:10:13,237
Saya bukan kedekut.

168
00:10:13,904 --> 00:10:17,199
Saya cuma tak percayakan dia.

169
00:10:17,283 --> 00:10:20,036
- Siapa?
- Presiden Kizashi.

170
00:10:20,119 --> 00:10:22,246
Dia cakap besar,

171
00:10:22,330 --> 00:10:24,165
tapi tak bersemangat…

172
00:10:24,248 --> 00:10:25,750
Saya rasa dia cuma menunjuk-nunjuk.

173
00:10:25,833 --> 00:10:27,501
Tapi dia hebat.

174
00:10:27,585 --> 00:10:29,795
Sesiapa pun boleh nampak hebat

175
00:10:29,879 --> 00:10:32,715
kalau mereka ada duit dan masa lapang.
Sesiapa pun boleh.

176
00:10:32,798 --> 00:10:35,176
- Yakah?
- Aduhai…

177
00:10:35,259 --> 00:10:37,762
Mestilah boleh, paling kurang pun begitu.

178
00:10:38,304 --> 00:10:41,474
- Pn. Enjaku, jom!
- Okey, ayuh.

179
00:10:41,557 --> 00:10:43,476
Sedia, mula!

180
00:10:46,395 --> 00:10:47,772
Jangan panaskan pundi kencing orang.

181
00:10:47,855 --> 00:10:50,733
- Apa rasanya?
- Ia satu perasaan baharu.

182
00:10:51,275 --> 00:10:52,777
- Jangan buat saya gelak!
- Fokus!

183
00:10:53,861 --> 00:10:54,737
Mula!

184
00:10:55,821 --> 00:10:56,947
Lagi!

185
00:11:00,117 --> 00:11:01,118
Masa… Tamat!

186
00:11:02,953 --> 00:11:04,163
Keputusannya…

187
00:11:04,246 --> 00:11:06,749
Ini rekod baharu. 35.6 darjah!

188
00:11:06,832 --> 00:11:09,835
- Wah!
- Ya! Naik satu darjah!

189
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:11,962
Suhu badan manusia!

190
00:11:13,130 --> 00:11:15,341
Aman betul.

191
00:11:15,424 --> 00:11:19,136
Minum pada siang hari,
berlatih gunakan kuasa tak berguna,

192
00:11:19,220 --> 00:11:22,473
dibayar untuk kutip sampah…

193
00:11:22,556 --> 00:11:24,308
Itukah wira moden kita?

194
00:11:24,392 --> 00:11:26,977
- Bolehkah kita santai begini?
- Kalau tak suka, berhentilah.

195
00:11:27,061 --> 00:11:29,939
Tak suka? Mustahil!

196
00:11:30,022 --> 00:11:33,859
Malah, saya kesal
sebab tak jumpa kerja begini lebih awal.

197
00:11:33,943 --> 00:11:35,486
- Satu lagi!
- Buatlah sendiri.

198
00:11:35,569 --> 00:11:36,445
Baik, tuan.

199
00:11:38,155 --> 00:11:41,075
Saya langsung tak faham
makna menjadi wira.

200
00:11:41,575 --> 00:11:44,036
Apa pentingnya setiap misi kita?

201
00:11:51,752 --> 00:11:54,255
- Nak saya buat untuk awak juga?
- Tak nak, tak apa.

202
00:11:54,338 --> 00:11:56,132
- Tak susah pun.
- Sungguh,

203
00:11:56,215 --> 00:11:58,300
saya tak sanggup suruh awak buat.

204
00:11:59,802 --> 00:12:00,636
Apa?

205
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:12,982
- Ohsuke, awak ada cakap apa-apa lagi?
- Apa?

206
00:12:13,065 --> 00:12:16,026
Awak beritahu dia
yang saya pembunuh lagi, ya?

207
00:12:16,569 --> 00:12:18,779
- Tengok!
- Tengok!

208
00:12:19,613 --> 00:12:21,407
Sudah-sudahlah!

209
00:12:21,490 --> 00:12:22,950
- Tak betulkah?
- Mestilah tak!

210
00:12:23,033 --> 00:12:25,870
- Tapi awak hampir-hampir bunuh dia.
- Ya, hampir-hampir.

211
00:12:25,953 --> 00:12:27,830
Mujurlah dia selamat.

212
00:12:27,913 --> 00:12:31,083
Dulu Hanzo seorang polis.

213
00:12:31,167 --> 00:12:33,711
- Pegawai polis?
- Unit K-9.

214
00:12:37,089 --> 00:12:39,175
Tolong rahsiakannya.
Saya tak suka bercakap mengenainya.

215
00:12:39,258 --> 00:12:41,469
Dia belasah lelaki yang dera anjing.

216
00:12:41,552 --> 00:12:43,387
Lebih teruk daripada itu!

217
00:12:43,471 --> 00:12:45,514
Dia sumbat 50 anjing

218
00:12:45,598 --> 00:12:47,516
dalam bilik kecil untuk biakkan mereka.

219
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:49,518
Saya laporkan dia kepada bos saya
dan Jabatan Kawalan Haiwan,

220
00:12:49,602 --> 00:12:51,061
tapi mereka kata tak dapat buat apa-apa.

221
00:12:53,147 --> 00:12:54,273
Betul tak?

222
00:12:55,774 --> 00:12:56,942
Keadaan waktu itu teruk.

223
00:12:57,651 --> 00:12:59,320
Saya pecah masuk ke bilik itu

224
00:12:59,403 --> 00:13:01,989
dan bebaskan semua anjing,

225
00:13:02,615 --> 00:13:05,993
tapi saya tertangkap separuh jalan
dan saya lawan balik.

226
00:13:06,785 --> 00:13:09,705
- Awak hampir-hampir bunuh dia?
- Ya.

227
00:13:10,456 --> 00:13:12,249
Anjing-anjing itu selamat,

228
00:13:12,333 --> 00:13:15,419
tapi saya dipecat dan dipenjarakan.

229
00:13:15,503 --> 00:13:17,922
Waktu itu saya yakin saya dapat seru.

230
00:13:18,547 --> 00:13:19,757
Waktu itu,

231
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:23,135
- awak belum jadi Esper, bukan?
- Belum.

232
00:13:23,802 --> 00:13:26,222
Tapi dari dulu saya berharap

233
00:13:27,264 --> 00:13:29,975
saya dapat faham perasaan haiwan.

234
00:13:31,977 --> 00:13:32,895
Mereka kata

235
00:13:33,479 --> 00:13:35,981
E-Kapsul itu ubah kebolehan kita
mengikut perwatakan,

236
00:13:37,107 --> 00:13:39,568
tapi mungkin kapsul itu cerminkan
hajat paling mendalam kita.

